Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:26.12,Lyrics EN,,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,—Episode 002—\NThe gamble for tomorrow{NOTE:明日に賭ける}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:02:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,One-two! One-two!\NOne-two! One-two!{NOTE:一二。一二。一二。一二。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore.{NOTE:あーもうダメ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing yet.{NOTE:なに言ってんの、これぐらいで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, stand up.{NOTE:さ、立って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.{NOTE:苦しいも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough too.{NOTE:あたしはもうダメ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't get you anywhere. Come on, stand up.{NOTE:ダメダメ、こんなことじゃ。さ、立って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about we run somewhere else without sand?{NOTE:ね、XXX砂XXXましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,While it'd feel easier, running on sand is the best for training your legs.{NOTE:XXXだからいいのよ。足腰お鍛えには砂地はが一番もの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, one more lapse to the lighthouse.{NOTE:さ。あの灯台までもうXXXよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That far…?{NOTE:はーあんな遠くまで？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together. Our opponents are volleyball club's regulars.{NOTE:しっかりして。相手はバレー部のレギュラーよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If we admit defeat here, we'll never win.{NOTE:このぐらいで値を上げてたら、勝ってこないでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as the chief says.{NOTE:そうよ。親分の言う通りだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep at it until we pass out.{NOTE:やるといったら、死ぬまでやるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, exactly.{NOTE:そのいち。そのいち。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go!{NOTE:じゃ。出発行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… wait…{NOTE:あー待って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me…{NOTE:まってよー}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best.{NOTE:さ。皆頑張って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hara-san, here I go.{NOTE:ハラさん,行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hara-san, pull yourself together.{NOTE:あ。ほら、ハラさん、しっかりやって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,– I'm sorry.\N– Isn't this enough?{NOTE:—すみません。\\N—XXXこのぐらいにしたら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.{NOTE:ダメダメ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad if you start thinking that way.{NOTE:XXX様そんなこと言っちゃ困るじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But our opponents are just a bunch of newcomers.{NOTE:でも、相手は白いと同然の不良グループよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they could win with us.{NOTE:XXX立って勝ってないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.{NOTE:油断は禁物。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We've no idea what Ayuhara-san's plans might be.{NOTE:あゆはらさんはなにを考えてるか警戒しないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.{NOTE:それは大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be doing her best, but…{NOTE:彼女が一人頑張ったって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,…you can't say that about the others.{NOTE:ほかる五人はXXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One-two! One-two!\NOne-two! One-two!{NOTE:一二。一二。一二。一二。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do this.{NOTE:さ、頑張って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should quit.{NOTE:もう辞めちゃう、あたしは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I keep at this, I'll pass out for real.{NOTE:これ以上やったら、本当に死んじゃうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Again? What's with that attitude?{NOTE:また。あんたたち、そんなXX気がどうすんなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Last few steps.{NOTE:さ、立って。最後まで頑張るのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it.{NOTE:もうたくさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like volleyball is impossible for us after all.{NOTE:XXX、バレーなんかあたしたちに無理だったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Our opponents are genuine volleyball club members. I'm hungry all t—{NOTE:そうよ。相手はほんとうのバレー部たち。やるXXXきゃむりよ。お腹がすく—}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you serious about this?{NOTE:ちょっと、あんたたち、それ本気？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Go-go dancing is much more fun.{NOTE:そうだよ。こんあことしてらXXXゴゴXXX楽しいXXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?{NOTE:ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so soft, you two.{NOTE:二人とも、甘ったれないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Nakazawa-san.{NOTE:まって、なかざわさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But those two…{NOTE:でも、あんまり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Leave it to me.{NOTE:いいから。あたしに任してちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit me all you want.{NOTE:XXXけもっとXXXいいわ。／打ちだけもっと打てばいいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I quit.{NOTE:とにかく、あたしXXXもらうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… wait…{NOTE:あー待って}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, what do we do?{NOTE:親分、どうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?{NOTE:あなたたちこそ、どうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm all alone, I'll still do it.{NOTE:あたしはたとえ一人なったってやるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,– Me too.\N– Of course me too.{NOTE:—あたしも。\\N—もちろん、あたしも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's continue then.{NOTE:じゃ、やりましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They will come to their senses soon enough.{NOTE:あのふたりともきっとそのうち分かってくれるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,– All right. Let's continue.\N– We'll go on with just the 4 of us.{NOTE:—うん。やるわ。\\N—XXXなったら、四人だっていいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.24,Alternative,,0,0,0,,But we can't play with just 4 people.{NOTE:でも四人でバレーはできない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.10,Alternative,,0,0,0,,It'll be bad if I don't get them back.{NOTE:あのふたりをなんとかしなきゃ大変なことになるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. It's still too early to give up.{NOTE:んん。しかし、諦めるのはまだ早いじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of giving up, but…{NOTE:もちろんあたしだって完全に諦めたわけじゃないけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of them have already dropped out of training.{NOTE:トレーニング大事に決めで脱落XXXのふたりも出ちゃう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in myself.{NOTE:とても自身ないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With things like this, shouldn't you forfeit the match?{NOTE:じゃ、バレー部に試合中止をもうしれるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame, but… I guess…{NOTE:残念だけど、そう言うことに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you'll be only giving the\hother girls false hopes, Ayuhara-kun.{NOTE:でも、それじゃ…彼女達をXXXさせるだけだよ、あゆはらくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like my plan was absurd to begin with.{NOTE:元々、あたしの計画は無理だったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weak. It doesn't suit you.{NOTE:弱きだな。きみらしくないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's impossible to hold a match with just 4 people.{NOTE:だって、四人でどうにも試合にはならないもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:—はい。\\N—XXX。\\N—はい。それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best. One more time.{NOTE:頑張って。もう一つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it.{NOTE:頑張って。さ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. By the way, volleyball club's practice seems to be more intense lately.{NOTE:なるほど。そう言えば、バレー部の練習はいつもと違います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because they don't want to lose to the Kashiwagi's group.{NOTE:いじでも、かしわぎやなかざまグループに負けたくないからでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is Ayuhara Kozue staying with these delinquents, I wonder.{NOTE:しかし、あゆはらこずえもなんであんな不良グループのかたおもつんでしょうな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it myself.{NOTE:分かりませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She transferred from Meihou Academy after all.{NOTE:めいほう学園から来たXXXしてはXXXますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Ultimately, volleyball isn't her only redeeming feature.{NOTE:そ、そそそ。結局取り柄はバレーだけって子じゃないですか、あゆはらこずえは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Meihou Academy, you say?{NOTE:え？めいほう学園ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The one in Tokyo that only accepts the best among the best students. That Meihou Academy.{NOTE:そうなのよ。東京でも仲裁XXXの秀才が集まってる。あのめいほう学園よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, their volleyball club must be famous too?{NOTE:じゃ、バレー部も有名な名門校よ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she made fun of us.{NOTE:分かったわ。それだあたしたちバレー部をバカにしたんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let our guard down.{NOTE:そうなると、XXX油断できないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't believe it.{NOTE:でも信じられないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For her to be a Meihou's prodigy…{NOTE:彼女はめいほうの秀才だなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the best school has its worst students.{NOTE:いくらいい学校でもピンからキリまでいるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like our Fujimi Academy.{NOTE:わが富士見学園のようにね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. With that in mind, perhaps Ayuhara-san got expelled.{NOTE:そうよ。だからあゆはらさんもしかしたら退学処分にでもなって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, listen, listen.\NGot news.{NOTE:ね、ちょっとちょっとちょっと。聞いた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san got expelled from Meihou Academy.{NOTE:あゆはらさんってめいほう学園X退学処分になった人何だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that she came to our school, she started hanging out with the delinquents.{NOTE:え。それでここへ来ても不良グループと付き合ってのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.{NOTE:ちょっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?{NOTE:あんたたち今なんて言ったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? N-Nothing.{NOTE:え？え…なー何も…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we called you delinquents.{NOTE:べつにあなたたちのこと不良グループって言ってわけじゃ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.{NOTE:そんなこと聞いてないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hear that Ayuhara-san was expelled?{NOTE:あゆはらさんは退学処分なったと話どこから聞いたXXX言うのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Err… from a member of the volleyball club.{NOTE:あの…それはバレー部の人から。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?{NOTE:なんですって}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Everyone!{NOTE:ね、ね！ちょっと皆！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Naka?{NOTE:どうしたのよ、ナカ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,– We're gonna show the volleyball club.\N– Wait, what?{NOTE:—バレー部…殴り込むよ。\\N—バレー部へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See, they're telling a story that Ayuhara-san was expelled from a school in Tokyo.{NOTE:そうよ。あの連中ったらね、あゆはらさんは東京の学校退学処分なんて声がXXXなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're spreading this rumor to everyone.{NOTE:皆に言い触らしちゃってのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let it slide any longer. Come with me.{NOTE:もう勘弁できないわ。あんたたちも来て。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go too?{NOTE:いこう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll still do it.{NOTE:でもやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up till the very end.{NOTE:あたし最後まで諦めないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,One does what one can do.{NOTE:人事を尽くして、天命を待つか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Chief, this is bad!{NOTE:おい。親分、大変よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Naka and the others went to attack the volleyball club. What do we do?{NOTE:あのね、ナカXXXたちわね、バレー部に殴り込むかけに行っちゃったXXX。どうする。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I'll go and see.{NOTE:え？あたし行ってみる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.94,Sign,,0,0,0,,Volleyball club's room{NOTE:バレー部}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you go around saying whatever you please?{NOTE:さ、皆、なんとか言ったらどうなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with calling expulsion for what it is.{NOTE:なによ。退学なった人は退学なったって何が悪いのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she was expelled, that's no reason to spread it.{NOTE:でも、何もそんな言い触らしないでもいいでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we're spreading rumors on purpose. It spread naturally.{NOTE:別に言い触らしたりしないわ。ただ自然に噂を広がっただけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's nothing to be upset about.{NOTE:そうよ。おこることないでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,People now understand that Ayuhara-san is a fitting boss for your group.{NOTE:あゆはらさんはあなたたちのグループのボスに相応しい人だってこと分かったんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are some big words.{NOTE:そんなことXXXわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'll fix this once and for all.{NOTE:今日はどうしても決着付けるから。思って出て。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of it.{NOTE:さ。飽きれたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can't beat us in volleyball, you're going to resort to violence, huh?{NOTE:暴力に訴えるXXXね、バレーでXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.{NOTE:そのとおりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball is such a boring game anyway.{NOTE:バレーなんかあんな面倒くさいゲームだってもうごめんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already out.{NOTE:あたしはもう辞めたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, is that so.{NOTE:おや、ま、そうなの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really quit?{NOTE:是非XXX辞めにしたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't care about Ayuhara-san, then?{NOTE:だったら、あゆはらさんから人事挨拶だってもういいじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't decided whether to quit yet.{NOTE:未だ辞めたって決めたわけじゃないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. Family trouble already?{NOTE:あら、あら。もう内輪もめ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball is so out of reach for you girls.{NOTE:こんな女子XXXとてもバレーは無理ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it!{NOTE:うるさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,– What do you know!\N– What are you doing?{NOTE:—XXX!\\N—何してんのXXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!{NOTE:待って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,– Ayuhara-san.\N– I heard about it from Kashiwagi-san.{NOTE:—あゆはらさん。\\N—事情はかしわぎさんから聞いたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But resorting to the violence is low.{NOTE:でも、暴力に訴えるなんて卑怯よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.{NOTE:卑怯でもなんだって、いいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong. The moment you lose your cool, you lose.{NOTE:ダメ。事情はXXX手を出したら負けよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But fine, be my guest.{NOTE:そんなことしてごらんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get expelled in return.{NOTE:XXXとあなたたちは退学よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, you'll play right into volleyball club's hand.{NOTE:それじゃ、バレー部の人達の思うツボじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're so impudent.{NOTE:だって、あんまりXXXだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.{NOTE:分かるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But vent your feelings in the match.{NOTE:でも、その気持ちを今度の試合ぶっつけるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?{NOTE:ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?{NOTE:分かってくれる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as the chief says.{NOTE:親分の言う通りよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone. Let's save our chief's\hface and withdraw for now, okay?{NOTE:ね、皆。この部は親分の顔ほ立てって,私達は引き上げることにしない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.{NOTE:いいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head back.{NOTE:XXXしてちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll surely settle this.{NOTE:じゃ。この決着は必ず付けて見せるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You better remember it.{NOTE:あんたたち、覚えていらっしゃい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo.{NOTE:んだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo.{NOTE:んだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Booo!{NOTE:ベーダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I calmed them down.{NOTE:XXXでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:ふん。さすがあゆはらさんですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She must regard herself as a good chief.{NOTE:いい子XXXおもって、XXXこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:あら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Ikezaki-san and Ooki-san go?{NOTE:池崎さんと大木さんはどこに行ったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.{NOTE:やっぱりダメ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They allied for the quarrel, but\htheir decision didn't change.{NOTE:喧嘩なら、見方するけど、バレーはごめんですって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.{NOTE:そ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not giving up yet.{NOTE:でもあたしは諦めないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mess…{NOTE:でも、あの様子じゃ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up.{NOTE:んん。諦めない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll persist till the very end.{NOTE:最後の最後まで、あたしは粘っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,– Good morning.\N– Good morning.{NOTE:—おはよう。\\N—おはよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,– Morning.\N– Good morning.{NOTE:—おはよう。\\N—おはよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:あら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?{NOTE:なにかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Midterm tests results are in.{NOTE:あ。中間テストの成績発表よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It only shows the best results though.{NOTE:うん。ベストXXXけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't concern us, does it.{NOTE:あたしたち縁のない話ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen! Big news!{NOTE:ちょっと、大変よ。大ニュース。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san has the highest score.{NOTE:あゆはらさんはテストに一番成ったんのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's ridiculous.{NOTE:え？そんなバカな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't deceive us.{NOTE:XXXってダメよ。／担ぐXXXってダメよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:55.48,Sign,,0,0,0,,Midterm tests results\NFirst place: Ayuhara Kozue{NOTE:中門テスト成績発表\\N一番鮎原こずえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth. Come see for yourself.{NOTE:本当よ。それでXXXじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. She's right.{NOTE:あ。本当。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san is the first.{NOTE:あゆはらさんは一番だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow…{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of method did you study with?{NOTE:一体どんな勉強したの?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing particular.{NOTE:さ、別に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun.{NOTE:あゆはらくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, I've been the first all the time.{NOTE:僕は…今までずっと一番だったんだぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Having you, a delinquent, surpass me…{NOTE:それを…エスケープのイメージの君に向かれるなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.{NOTE:信じられないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd pull it off.{NOTE:そんなバカなことってないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very fishy.{NOTE:絶対可笑しいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishy how?{NOTE:可笑しいってどう言うこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She means you must have done something.{NOTE:何かやったんじゃないかってことさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?{NOTE:なにか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. For example, you cheated.{NOTE:え。例えば、カンニングとか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?{NOTE:なんですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude.{NOTE:失礼なこと言わないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If you make such statements about our chief, we won't stand by idle.{NOTE:そうよ。カンニングがなんて…あたしたちの親分に変なXXX承知しないから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about you say something.{NOTE:ちょっと。なんとか言ったらどうなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof that I cheated?{NOTE:あたしは、カンニングしたって証拠でもあるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have.{NOTE:あるさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?{NOTE:だってそうだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,After expulsion from the Meihou Academy, no matter how different our level is…{NOTE:めいほう学園を退学処分になった君は、いくら程度が違うからって、}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,…there's no way you'd suddenly get the best score.{NOTE:この学校へ来て、急に一番とれるわけないじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My. When did I get expelled from anywhere?{NOTE:ま。何時あたしが退学処分になんかなって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's not how it was? Then, I…{NOTE:それはそうじゃないかった、あたしの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa. You guys.{NOTE:おい、おい。君達。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say rude things.{NOTE:失礼なこと言っちゃいかんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor…{NOTE:先生…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun always stood\hat\hthe\htop in the Meihou Academy.{NOTE:あゆはらくんはめいほう学園でずっと首席XXX人だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At the top—{NOTE:ま、首席—}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying she cheated was very rude.{NOTE:カンニングなんて失礼もういいとこだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome.{NOTE:すげー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, Mimura-san.{NOTE:XXXさん。お気の毒様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm in shock. For her to be at\hthe\htop of the Meihou Academy…{NOTE:ああ、あたしはショックだわ。あの人はめいほう学園の首席だなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like we've made fools of ourselves.{NOTE:丸であたしたちはバカみたいじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Now that it came to this, let's\hshow our strength through volleyball to her.{NOTE:よし。こうなったら、せめてバレーでXXXわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We mustn't lose to them.{NOTE:そうよ。どんなことXXX、負けられないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She tricked us after all.{NOTE:やっぱりあたしたちの騙されてたなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's plenty dignified without being our chief.{NOTE:なによ貫禄十分の親分よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally different from us.{NOTE:全然あたしたちのXXX違うじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But life sure is strange. I didn't see it coming at all.{NOTE:でも不思議だわ。そんなXXX全然見えないもう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing gathered like that?{NOTE:どうしたの？こんな所に集まって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this… we're, you know…{NOTE:あ、それは…いや、全然いいじゃない…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting strange.{NOTE:変XXXあなたたち。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But sure you're cruel, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:でも、酷いわ、あゆはらさんも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?{NOTE:なにが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you hiding your status at Meihou Academy.{NOTE:だって、めいほう学園の大秀才だってこと…あたしたちに隠したりしてさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not like I've been hiding it out of malice.{NOTE:あら、別に隠したりなんかしてないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that if I haven't stayed\hsilent, it'd come across as boasting.{NOTE:ただ、そんなこと自慢にもならないから黙ってだけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're in a different world from us.{NOTE:でも、あなたはあたしたちと別世界の人よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A prodigy like you has no business in hanging out with losers like us.{NOTE:XXX大秀才XXXあたしたちXXXには付き合いXXXわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying this seriously?{NOTE:あなたたち本気そんなこと言ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That we can't be friends just because I happen to have good grades?{NOTE:退学になったころ仲間で首席じゃだめなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I am me. Ayuhara Kozue.{NOTE:あたしはあたし。あゆはらこずえよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we going to take on the volleyball club together?{NOTE:一緒にバレー部やっつけるおとしじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that so?{NOTE:ね、そうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,– But…\N– Do you really mean it?{NOTE:—でも…\\N—本当にそう思う？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If I didn't, I wouldn't be able to befriend you to begin with.{NOTE:え。それでなきゃ最初からあなたたちとお友達してないかならないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't care about our training or your club assault either.{NOTE:悔しい思いXXXして殴り込みを止めたりなんかしないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm touched.{NOTE:ああ、感激。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's truly our chief.{NOTE:やっぱりあたしたちの親分だわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we can hang around like we used to?{NOTE:じゃ、今までXXX付き合ってXXXね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.{NOTE:もちろんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikezaki-san. Ooki-san.{NOTE:池崎さん。大木さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we make up and be friends again?{NOTE:あなたたちともう一度考え直して、お友達になってくれない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Us too? Wah…{NOTE:あたしたちも？わ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?{NOTE:どう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooki-san.{NOTE:大木さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you too want to beat the volleyball club?{NOTE:あなたたちだってバレー部をぎゃふんといらせたいでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you too came during the assault, no?{NOTE:だから殴り込みの時にとんできたでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Training sure is hard.{NOTE:XXXトレーニングは苦しいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But we need to overcome its hardship.{NOTE:でも、この苦しいに乗り越えなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikezaki-san. Ooki-san.{NOTE:池崎さん。大木さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,– Okay.\N– I'll do it too.{NOTE:—いいわ、あたし。\\N—あたしもやるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you forgive us?{NOTE:あたしたちのこと許してくれる?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to forgive.{NOTE:許すなんて、そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all on the same page.{NOTE:あたしたち皆同じよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The strength lies in teamwork.{NOTE:一人かけてもダメよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah. I'm happy.{NOTE:わ。嬉しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't make fun of good students like you anymore.{NOTE:あんたみたいに秀才の仲間XXXもうバカにするないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Now all that's left is to train.{NOTE:そうよ。後はバレーだけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Now that it's decided, let's do our best.{NOTE:よし。そうと決まったら、皆、頑張ろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No quitting midway, got it?{NOTE:絶対途中音を上げないのよ。いいわ、ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, from today, it's one month of strict training.{NOTE:じゃ、今日から一ヶ月みっちりトレーニングよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?{NOTE:いいわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,– Okay!\N– Okay!{NOTE:—OK！\\N—OK！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.19,Alternative,,0,0,0,,This should be good.{NOTE:これでいいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.24,Alternative,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to win the match.{NOTE:後試合を勝つだけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:07.40,Alternative,,0,0,0,,If we win, it will give these girls the confidence they need and everything will go well.{NOTE:そうすれば、この人達だって自身が付くし、何もかもうまくいくわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One-two! One-two!\NOne-two! One-two!{NOTE:一二！一二！一二！一二！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. From today we'll focus on handling the ball.{NOTE:さ！じゃ、いよいよ今日からボールをつかっての練習よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one rule to winning.{NOTE:敵に勝つ方法がただ一つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's practice. Practice. Practice!{NOTE:練習。練習。練習よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,– Got it?\N– Yeah.{NOTE:—分かったわね？\\N—うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. Nakazawa-san, here I go.{NOTE:じゃ、なかざわさん、いくわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,– Okay.\N– Naka, do your best!{NOTE:—OK。\\N—ナカ、頑張って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.{NOTE:ダメ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In 6-player volleyball, if you let yourself lose the ball, it's a foul play.{NOTE:六人制のバレーではどんな場合でも、パチンなんと落とさせたら、犯則よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass must be done with the fingertips.{NOTE:パスは必ず指先で弾く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.{NOTE:OK。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's do it in turns.{NOTE:じゃ、往復、行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,– It hurts.\N– I'm sorry.{NOTE:—あ—痛い。\\N—ごめん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.81,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Good.{NOTE:いいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:16.55,Alternative,,0,0,0,,If they stay this inspired for\ha\hmonth, we might make it.{NOTE:これだけファイトXXXば一ヶ月でも間に合えるかもしれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't cut it.{NOTE:ダメダメ、そんなことじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here goes!{NOTE:じゃ、いくわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!{NOTE:じゃ、頑張って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll focus on serving and receiving.{NOTE:今日はサーブとサーブレシーブの練習よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In 6-player system, you only get one serve, so aim to hit the ball into the opponents court.{NOTE:六人制ではサーブは一回しか打てないから、確実に相手のコートに入れること。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,– Got it?\N– Yeah.{NOTE:—いい？\\N—うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull it together.{NOTE:しっかり、しっかり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, stand up.{NOTE:ほら、XXX／頑張って。／立って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.27,Alternative,,0,0,0,,They're really giving their best.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:15.02,Alternative,,0,0,0,,These girls are full of potential.{NOTE:この女子だと何か行けるかもしれないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.{NOTE:痛い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my finger twisted to the right.{NOTE:あ、指が右に倒れた。XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you saying.{NOTE:え？何言ってるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a jammed finger.{NOTE:ただの突き指よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll normal to have all 10 fingers jammed at once.{NOTE:うまくなるには突き指の十回ぐらいは普通よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? All 10?{NOTE:え？十回も？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, my beautiful fingers will get all lumpy.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to joke.{NOTE:冗談言ってる場合はないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got three weeks before the match.{NOTE:バレー部と試合まであと三週間。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Those with jammed fingers, switch to jumping until healing. Got it?{NOTE:突き指した人は治るまでジャンプの練習よ。いいわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be at it.{NOTE:中々やるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The others are pathetic though.{NOTE:この低能なら大したことないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they'd win with just one month of training.{NOTE:そうよ。一月の練習で我々に勝ってるわけがないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. It's the volleyball club.{NOTE:あ。バレー部の連中よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.{NOTE:ふん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They came to spy on us.{NOTE:検察に来たんだ、きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pay attention to them.{NOTE:だれが身に来いXXX気にしない、気にしない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's begin.{NOTE:さ、始めて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,– They'll be the same during the match.\N– Yeah.{NOTE:—試合なんかやるだけもXXX。\\N—そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.{NOTE:ふん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you want.{NOTE:何とでも言いなさいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You'll pay if you underestimate us.{NOTE:そうよ。人を舐めると承知しないから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and practice.{NOTE:黙って。練習する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They say such things because they're scared.{NOTE:あんなこと言うな、自分たちが不安だから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Begin, begin!{NOTE:さ、始めて、始めて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,– Professor Hongou.\N– Hm?{NOTE:—ほんごう先生。\\N—は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about those girls?{NOTE:あの子たちのこと。どう考えXXXすの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm probably thinking the same thing as you do.{NOTE:XXX,おそらく、あなたと同じこと考えています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My…{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Ayuhara-kun started coaching volleyball…{NOTE:あゆはらくんがバレーのコーチを始めてからってもな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,…their diligence in the classroom and their grades have improved.{NOTE:…教室であの彼女達の怠惰や成績は見違えるようによくなった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps with her help, the girls will get back on the right track.{NOTE:と言うことは、きっと…バレーな彼女達を精神的に立ち直れすXXXかもしれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so too?{NOTE:そうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.{NOTE:その通りですわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As her homeroom teacher, I'm\htaking my hat off to Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:あたしXX担任として、あゆはらさん脱帽したい気持ちです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same.{NOTE:いや。まったく同感ですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But professor, let's not engage\hyet and keep watching over her.{NOTE:しかし先生、もう少し黙ってみてやりましょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be set on winning with the volleyball club.{NOTE:彼女は今、XXX,真剣にバレーに打ち込んじるんですから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it!{NOTE:XXX,頑張ってよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time!{NOTE:もう行くよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, do your best!{NOTE:頑張って、頑張って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.76,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Three days left.{NOTE:後三日。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:33.86,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Now that they mastered basic techniques, the match is on.{NOTE:技術XXXできるはこのファイトXXXだけわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:36.51,Alternative,,0,0,0,,We will win without fail.{NOTE:絶対に…絶対に勝って見せるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Tsutomu-chan? Kozue-chan plays volleyball?{NOTE:なんですって、つとむちゃん？こずえちゃんはバレーボールを？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She took the entire volleyball club on.{NOTE:バレー部相手にやるんだって、XXXよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why she's been coming late recently.{NOTE:とれで、このごろ毎日帰りにな遅かったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie, you didn't know?{NOTE:叔母さんは知らなかったか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How was I supposed to?{NOTE:知るもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure she was studying in the library every day.{NOTE:毎日図書館で勉強してるとばかり思ってたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah– damn.{NOTE:あーしまったな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please keep it a secret that I told you.{NOTE:じゃ、僕から聞いたこと…内緒にしといてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.{NOTE:そうは行けませんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue-chan's body won't withstand volleyball.{NOTE:こずえちゃんはバレー何かやっては行けない体なのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that bad?{NOTE:そんなに悪いの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.{NOTE:当たり前じゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, why'd she come all the way here in the middle of the school term.{NOTE:でなきゃ、態々こんな所へ???来るもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But she looks so full of energy—{NOTE:でも、あんなに元気なのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it just by looking at her face.{NOTE:顔だけ見たって分かるもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a responsible boy.\NWhy didn't you tell me earlier?{NOTE:あなたはあなたもうじゃないの。なぜもっと早く知らせてくれないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Err…{NOTE:おー}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.{NOTE:すみません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sorry" doesn't cut it.{NOTE:すみませんじゃすまないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue is the one that knows her own body the best.{NOTE:こずえ自分の体のことは自分が一番知っているだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I think it's okay.{NOTE:だから大丈夫だと思って…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't go.{NOTE:いかん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let it get any worse.{NOTE:もし悪化したら、大変だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the hospital at once.{NOTE:直ぐこれから病院へ行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's only one day before the match.{NOTE:でも、バレー部と試合まで後一日しかないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If I withdrew today, what would happen to Kashiwagi-san and our group?{NOTE:今、あたしはXXX引いたら、かしわぎさんたち、グループはどうなるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Group?{NOTE:グループ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.{NOTE:やもうえんだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That match cannot be this important.{NOTE:どうせいこんな試合なんて大したことあるない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.{NOTE:そんなことないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The tomorrow's match is very precious to me.{NOTE:明日の試合にはもっと大事なことかかってるんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so precious?{NOTE:大事なことってなんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's… err…{NOTE:それは…その…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kozue-chan.{NOTE:ね、こうぜちゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we need to take care of you too.{NOTE:とにかく、あなたは大事な預かりものなんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise how would we apologize to your mom and dad?{NOTE:パパやママたいして、なんと詫びすればいいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize? Don't you grumble now.{NOTE:お詫びなんて、そんな…ぐずぐず言ってないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,– Let's hurry and go see the doctor.\N– No!{NOTE:—早く、医者の所へ行こう。\\N—いやです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue!{NOTE:こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kozue-chan.{NOTE:ね、こずえちゃん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, right?{NOTE:分かったでしょう?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For time being, at least let's\htake a\hradiograph, okay?{NOTE:とにかく、お医者様の所いって、レントゲンを撮って貰いましょう、ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:31.14,Alternative,,0,0,0,,What should I do?{NOTE:どうしよう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:33.54,Alternative,,0,0,0,,What if something shows up on the radiograph…{NOTE:もしレントゲンにXXXあったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!{NOTE:あーはい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:42.30,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1780)}Fuji Hospital{NOTE:富士病院}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor is taking too long.{NOTE:先生遅すぎるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is pumping.{NOTE:ね、あたし…むー胸がドキドキして…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Worrying now won't do any good.{NOTE:お前がドキドキすることはXXXない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll know the results soon.{NOTE:もうすぐ結果を分かる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.{NOTE:落ち着くんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:56.28,Alternative,,0,0,0,,What will I do, if the results turn out to be a "no"?{NOTE:その結果な「ノ」出たら、どうしよう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:58.35,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Everything will be over.{NOTE:何もかも終わりだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:05.10,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kashiwagi-san's group's energy… their spirit… their hopes… our dream…{NOTE:あんなに張り切ってXXX柏木さんたちグループのXXXも動力も…希望も…皆の夢…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,0:23:10.92,Alternative,,0,0,0,,After they trusted me and followed me this far, how will I apologize to them?{NOTE:あたしを寝台して京間でついてきてくれた皆に…なんと言ったら謝ればいいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:あゆはらさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.{NOTE:お待たせしました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?{NOTE:いかがでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.{NOTE:先生…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:58.01,Alternative,,0,0,0,,The doctor's gaze over radiograph is long and inscrutable.{NOTE:レントゲン写真にじっと見る医者の表情は固い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:03.09,Alternative,,0,0,0,,However, the youthful devotion to volleyball seems to have helped in curing the illness.{NOTE:だが、バレーボールに打ち込んだ若い生命力は、見事に病気を直していたのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.09,0:24:10.40,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Finally, the day of the match. The useless group led by Kozue settles things out with the volleyball club.{NOTE:いよいよ試合の日。こずえの率いる不良チームたいバレー部の解決は嫌な上にも任侠呼んだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:14.97,Alternative,,0,0,0,,The extreme training spanning one month seems to have fruited, but…{NOTE:不良チームは、一ヶ月激しいトレーニングの成果をXXXだが、}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:18.01,Alternative,,0,0,0,,…the useless group tenses up in\hfront of a crowd of spectators.{NOTE:大勢の慣習の前にしてしっかり固くなり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:21.69,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Unfazed, the volleyball club has no intention of going easy.{NOTE:バレー部のなすがままに、とくてんはどんどんひらいていく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.69,0:24:27.09,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワン：「新キャプテン誕生」お楽しみに。}
